Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,========Avant========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群混蛋！
