Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\an5\pos(355,80)\fs80\be4}艾 斯 迪 斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\an4\pos(-20,75)\fscy200\fscx1300\be4}-
