Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\an5\pos(1028,80)\fs80\be4}卡 兹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\an4\pos(-150,75)\fscy200\fscx7100\be4}-
